[{"id":"a23417d5f9d5439ae5634a1ccabdd800","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Spam: For Mr. Jeffrey Epstein-MICHAEL CLAYTON 30th","date":"2007-09-24T19:55:23.000Z","formatted_date":"Sep 24, 2007","formatted_time":"7:55 PM","body":" \n \n \n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Peggy Siegal [mailto:peggy@peggysiegal.com] \nSent: Monday, September 24, 2007 3:53 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Spam: For Mr. Jeffrey Epstein-MICHAEL CLAYTON 30th\n\n\n \n<http://rs6.net/on.jsp?t=1101822347890.0.1101430287919.1189&ts=S0274&o=h\nttp://ui.constantcontact.com/images/p1x1.gif> \nPlease come join George Clooney, Tilda Swinton and Tony Gilroy at their\nintimate private screening of ?Michael Clayton.? No red carpet, no\npaparazzi, no press. It?s just a terrific low key Sunday night with the\nfilmmakers and their friends.\nxxoo\nPeggy\nWarner Bros. Pictures \nSamuels Media and Castle Rock Entertainment\ninvite you to join\nGeorge Clooney   Tilda Swinton\nand writer and director Tony Gilroy\nat a private screening of\nMICHAEL CLAYTON\nSunday, September 30, 2007\n7:00pm The Time Warner Theater\nOne Time Warner Center, 10th floor\nenter at 58th Street between 8th & 9th Avenues\n9:00pm dinner hosted by Edmiston & Company\nNicholas Edmiston, Chairman\n&\nDiego Marroquin, Vice President\nPorter House New York\n10 Columbus Circle, 4th floor\npeggy@peggysiegal.com or 212-935-6700\nthis invitation is non-transferable\nconfirmed guests\nBob Balaban\nTory Burch\nLauren Bush\nGeorge Clooney\nKenneth Cole\nWalter Cronkite\nTony Gilroy\nLara Spencer\nRobert Wood Johnson\nBill Keller\nJames Kelly\nJared Kushner\nMatt Lauer\nJulianna Margulies\nBennett Miller\nSam Newhouse\nPete Peterson\nNick Pileggi & Nora Ephron\nSteve Samuels\nHoward Schultz\nTilda Swinton\nVicky Ward\nStrauss Zelnick\nMichael Clayton (GEORGE CLOONEY) is an in-house ?fixer? at one of the\nlargest corporate law firms in New York.  A former criminal prosecutor,\nClayton takes care of Kenner, Bach & Ledeen?s dirtiest work at the\nbehest of the firm?s co-founder Marty Bach (SYDNEY POLLACK).  Though\nburned out and hardly content with his job, his divorce, a failed\nbusiness venture and mounting debt have left Clayton inextricably tied\nto the firm.  \n            At U/North, meanwhile, the career of litigator Karen Crowder\n(TILDA SWINTON) rests on the multi-million dollar settlement of a class\naction suit that Clayton?s firm is leading to a seemingly successful\nconclusion.  But when Kenner Bach?s brilliant and guilt-ridden attorney\nArthur Edens (TOM WILKINSON) sabotages the U/North case, Clayton faces\nthe biggest challenge of his career and his life.\n\n \n<http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=un&m=1101430287919&se=1189&t\n=1101822347890&lang=en&reason=F>  \nThis email was sent to lesley@nysgllc.com, by peggy@peggysiegal.com\nUpdate Profile/Email Address\n<http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=oo&m=1101430287919&se=1189&t\n=1101822347890&lang=en&reason=F>  | Instant removal with SafeUnsubscribe\n<http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=un&m=1101430287919&se=1189&t\n=1101822347890&lang=en&reason=F> (tm) | Privacy Policy\n<http://ui.constantcontact.com/roving/CCPrivacyPolicy.jsp> .\n\t\n\nPeggy Siegal | 4 West 58th Street | mezzanine | New York | NY | 10019 \t\n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Please come join George Clooney, Tilda Swinton and Tony Gilroy at their intimate private screening of ?Michael Clayton</TITLE>\n<META http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<META content=Word.Document name=ProgId>\n<META content=\"MSHTML 6.00.3790.94\" name=GENERATOR>\n<META content=\"Microsoft Word 11\" name=Originator><LINK \nhref=\"Please%20come%20join%20George%20Clooney_files/fileli