nd mounting \ndebt have left Clayton inextricably tied to the firm.&nbsp; \n<O:P></O:P></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 4pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><O:P></O:P></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nAt U/North, meanwhile, the career of litigator Karen Crowder (TILDA SWINTON) \nrests on the multi-million dollar settlement of a class action suit that \nClayton?s firm is leading to a seemingly successful conclusion.&nbsp; But when \nKenner Bach?s brilliant and guilt-ridden attorney Arthur <SPAN \nclass=SpellE>Edens</SPAN> (TOM WILKINSON) sabotages the U/North case, Clayton \nfaces the biggest challenge of his career and his life.<O:P></O:P></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><O:P></O:P></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><O:P></O:P></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><O:P></O:P></SPAN></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><O:P></O:P></P></DIV><BR>\n<TABLE width=\"100%\" bgColor=#ffffff padding=\"0\">\n  <TBODY>\n  <TR align=middle>\n    <TD>\n      <TABLE width=595 bgColor=#ffffff>\n        <TBODY>\n        <TR>\n          <TD><FONT face=verdana,arial size=1><FOOTERCONTENT><A \n            href=\"http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=un&amp;m=1101430287919&amp;se=1189&amp;t=1101822347890&amp;lang=en&amp;reason=F\" \n            target=_blank shape=rect><IMG \n            src=\"http://img.constantcontact.com/letters/images/safe_unsubscribe_logo.gif\" \n            border=0 NOSEND=\"1\"></A> \n            <DIV>This email was sent to lesley@nysgllc.com, by <A \n            style=\"COLOR: #0000ff\" href=\"mailto:peggy@peggysiegal.com\" \n            shape=rect>peggy@peggysiegal.com</A></DIV>\n         